 & =nc+\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}(a_i+a_{i+1})\cdot S_i\\
 & =nc+\left[S_1S_0+(S_2-S_0)S_1+(S_3-S_1)S_2+\cdots+(S_n-S_{n-2})S_{n-1}\right]
\end{align*}
即$S_n^2-S_n+nc=0$, $\Delta\ge0\Longrightarrow c\le\frac{1}{4n}$.
